List all service

systemctl list-unit-files --type service

Enable service
chkconfig name on  
systemctl enable name.service

Disables a service.
chkconfig name off
systemctl disable name.service

Checks if a service is enabled.
chkconfig --list name
systemctl status name.service

Starts a service.
service name start
systemctl start name.service

service name stop
systemctl stop name.service
Stops a service.


systemctl enable smb 
systemctl disable smb 
systemctl start smb

systemctl status smb.service
systemctl list-unit-files

systemctl enable telnet.socket
systemctl start telnet.socket
systemctl stop telnet.socket
systemctl status telnet.socket

service samba status

systemctl disable firewalld
service firewalld stop
service firewalld start

Disable selinux

Disable virbr0

virsh net-undefine default

kernel loader change

grubby --default-kernel
grubby --default-index

look for kernel in /boot

grubby --set-default /boot/vmlinuz-3.10.0-229.4.2.el7.x86_64

Seeting hostname AWS Redhat 7

sudo hostnamectl set-hostname --static linuxpoc-2.test.lan
Add preserve_hostname: true in /etc/cloud/cloud.cfg



